<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cruz Azul ERP — Seguridad AAA</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav', { user: user, active: 'seguridad', instance: instance }) %>
  <div class="main">
    <div class="topbar">
      <h2>Seguridad AAA + MFA</h2>
      <div class="topbar-right">
        <span class="user-email"><%= user.email %></span>
        <span class="badge badge-info"><%= user.role %></span>
        <a class="logout-link" href="/logout">Cerrar sesión</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Authentication</h3>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-500)">Login con credenciales + emisión de JWT firmado. Rate limiting: 10 intentos/15min.</p>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Estado</span><span class="info-value"><span class="badge badge-success">Activo</span></span></div>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Token</span><span class="info-value">JWT · <%= jwtExpires %></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Authorization</h3>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-500)">Middleware que valida token y rol en cada ruta protegida.</p>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Tu rol</span><span class="info-value"><span class="badge badge-info"><%= user.role %></span></span></div>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Acceso</span><span class="info-value">Condicional por token (AAA)</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Accounting</h3>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-500)">Cada inicio de sesión se registra en BD con IP y timestamp.</p>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Registro</span><span class="info-value"><a href="/erp/logs">Ver logs →</a></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>MFA (TOTP)</h3>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-500)">Segundo factor opcional. Código de 6 dígitos vía app autenticadora.</p>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Estado</span><span class="info-value">
            <span class="badge <%= mfaEnabled ? 'badge-success' : 'badge-warning' %>">
              <%= mfaEnabled ? 'Habilitado' : 'Deshabilitado' %>
            </span>
          </span></div>
          <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Config</span><span class="info-value"><code>MFA_ENABLED=<%= mfaEnabled %></code></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="margin-top:16px">
        <h3>Modelo de seguridad por capas</h3>
        <div class="table-container">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Capa</th><th>Componente</th><th>Control</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Borde</td><td>ALB</td><td>SG-ALB: solo :80/:443 desde Internet</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Aplicación</td><td>EC2 Web ERP</td><td>SG-Web: solo :3000 desde SG-ALB · JWT · Rate limiting</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Datos</td><td>PostgreSQL</td><td>SG-DB: solo :5432 desde SG-Web · subred privada aislada</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Transversal</td><td>IAM / CloudWatch</td><td>AAA, MFA, alarmas, dashboard</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>